title: Claude Monet Water Lilies Pencil Set
description:
Pencil Set developed from Claude Monet’s Water Lilies (detail), 1906, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

Perfect for artists of all skill levels, this pencil set contains 12 colored pencils in a delightful printed box.  Give as a gift, or keep for your own drawings.

  • Set of 12 pencils.
  • Case Dimensions: 7 x 4 x .5 in.
  • Pencil Dimensions: 7 in.
  • Materials: Case – aluminum, Pencil – wood.
  • 12 colors.
